title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message appears when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
SR: Export a directory (project) and place the exported jar in the same directory (project). When overwriting the exported jar file for the second time, observe the appearance of an out of sync message.
